<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>{{subject}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px 0;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }

        .auction-details {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Your Auction Has Ended With No Bids</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p>Hello {{username}},</p>

        <p>We wanted to let you know that your auction for <strong>{{title}}</strong> has ended without receiving any
            bids.</p>

        <div class="auction-details">
            <h3>Auction Details:</h3>
            <p><strong>Starting Price:</strong> {{startingPrice}}</p>
            <p><strong>Category:</strong> {{category}}</p>
            <p><strong>Ended:</strong> {{endDate}}</p>

            <a href="{{auctionUrl}}" class="button">View Auction Ended</a>
        </div>

        <p>Here are some suggestions to help improve your chances of selling next time:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Consider adjusting your starting price to be more competitive</li>
            <li>Add more detailed descriptions and high-quality photos</li>
            <li>Review similar successful listings for pricing and description ideas</li>
            <li>Promote your listing on social media</li>
        </ul>

       <!-- <p>Would you like to relist this item? You can easily relist it from your dashboard.</p>

        <p style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="{{appUrl}}/dashboard/auctions/{{auctionId}}/relist" class="button">Relist This Item</a>
        </p>-->

        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>

        <p>Thank you for using {{appName}}!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>Â© {{year}} {{appName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p><a href="{{appUrl}}/support" style="color: #777; text-decoration: underline;">Contact Support</a></p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>